            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut </strong>and your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[320ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [420ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>coconut stock </strong>with your <strong>lime leaf[ves]</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
