        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat your <strong>cod fillet[s] </strong>dry with kitchen paper and season them with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>seasoned cod </strong>to the pan and cook, covered, for an initial 3-4 min</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
