        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 3-4 min, add your <strong>mangetout</strong> and cook, covered, for a further 3 min or until until the fish is cooked through and the veg has slightly softened – this is your <strong>fragrant Thai coconut cod with mangetout</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
