    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>fragrant Thai coconut cod with mangetout</strong> with the<strong> cooked rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with a good grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into small bowls and turn out</p>",
